author: Holly Ellyatt
title: Russia tries to stay neutral as US-China tensions rise over coronavirus' origin
description: Russia has sought to distance itself from a dispute brewing between the U.S. and China over the origin of the coronavirus, saying it can't support a U.S. investigation into the source of the virus.
content:
